Statement MatMult1x4{*A.matrix1x4, *B.matrix4x4, *R.matrix1x4}
; Mutltiplies one 1x4 matrix with 4x4 matrix. Result is 4x4.
; Uses global variables: ..._1x4*..._matrix->..._result
